  "texts": [
    "The MBFC label and the metadata of publishers is subject to change, as additional information is made available or corrections are processed.",
    "We list the 20 publishers whose labels changed substantively during the data collection period in Table B.6.",
    "In most instances, the label changed from reliable + to unreliable -due to additional fact check failures being incorporated into the MBFC database (12/20).",
    "The inverse also occurs, where publishers improve their editorial practices or correct articles that failed fact checks (5/20).",
    "Most metadata changes correspond to relatively minor changes in political bias (e.g., Left-Center to Right-Center), and do not alter the analyses presented in this article."
  ],
